data.description: Investor alert! All brick story and a half duplex. Each unit has 1,587 sf above, 3 beds with 1 on the main, 1.5 baths in 1 unit and 2 baths in the other, unfinished walk-up basement with laundry hookups in each side. Roof is 1 year old. Each side is $700 a month and tenants pay utilities and yard maintenance.
